<h1 class="text-center my-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

<div class="container mb-5">
    <!-- Section 1: Introduction -->
    <section class="mb-4">
        <h3>1. Introduction</h3>
        <p>
            Welcome to <strong>GrandShop</strong>. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data.
            This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website or make a purchase.
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 2: Information We Collect -->
    <section class="mb-4">
        <h3>2. Information We Collect</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number.</li>
            <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Username, password, and purchase history.</li>
            <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Credit/debit card details (handled securely).</li>
            <li><strong>Location Information:</strong> Shipping address for delivery purposes.</li>
            <li><strong>Browsing Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, cookies, and usage data.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3: How We Use Your Information -->
    <section class="mb-4">
        <h3>3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>To process your orders and provide delivery services.</li>
            <li>To communicate with you regarding your account, orders, or support requests.</li>
            <li>To improve our website, services, and user experience.</li>
            <li>To send you promotional offers, if you have opted-in.</li>
            <li>To comply with legal obligations and prevent fraud.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 4: Sharing Your Information -->
    <section class="mb-4">
        <h3>4. Sharing Your Information</h3>
        <p>We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties, except:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Payment processors, delivery companies, and hosting providers.</li>
            <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required to comply with laws or regulations.</li>
            <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> If GrandShop merges or is acquired, your information may be transferred.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 5: Cookies and Tracking Technologies -->
    <section class="mb-4">
        <h3>5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
        <p>We use cookies to improve your browsing experience, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> For core website functionality.</li>
            <li><strong>Performance Cookies:</strong> To analyze website usage and improve performance.</li>
            <li><strong>Marketing Cookies:</strong> For personalized ads and promotions.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You can manage or disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 6: Data Security -->
    <section class="mb-4">
        <h3>6. Data Security</h3>
        <p>
            We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information, including:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Encryption of sensitive data.</li>
            <li>Secure servers for storing information.</li>
            <li>Regular monitoring to prevent unauthorized access.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 7: Your Rights -->
    <section class="mb-4">
        <h3>7. Your Rights</h3>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information.</li>
            <li>Opt-out of receiving marketing communications.</li>
            <li>Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise your rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@grandshop.com">privacy@grandshop.com</a>.</p>
    </section>

